msgid "# Set-DfsrMember"
msgstr "# Set-DfsrMember"

msgid "## SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "## 概要"

msgid "Modifies member computer information in a replication group."
msgstr "修改复制组中成员计算机的信息。"

msgid "## SYNTAX"
msgstr "## 语法"

msgid "## DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "## 说明"

msgid ""
"The **Set-DfsrMember** cmdlet modifies member computer information in a replication group.\n"
"Members of a replication group host replicated folders.\n"
"You can modify the description of a member."
msgstr ""
"`Set-DfsrMember` cmdlet "
"用于修改复制组中成员计算机的信息。复制组的成员会托管被复制的文件夹，你可以更改这些成员的计算机描述（即相关属性）。"

msgid "## EXAMPLES"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid "### Example 1: Update the description for a member"
msgstr "#### 示例 1：更新成员的描述"

msgid ""
"This command updates the description for the computer named SRV01 in the group named RG07.\n"
"The console displays the **DfsrMember** object, which includes the updated description."
msgstr "此命令用于更新名为RG07的组中名为SRV01的计算机的描述信息。控制台会显示**DfsrMember**对象，其中包含更新后的描述内容。"

msgid "## PARAMETERS"
msgstr "## 参数"

msgid ""
"Specifies an array of names of member computers.\n"
"You can use a comma separated list and the wildcard character (*)."
msgstr "指定一组成员计算机的名称。你可以使用逗号分隔的列表以及通配符（*）。"

msgid "Prompts you for confirmation before running the cmdlet."
msgstr "在运行该cmdlet之前，会提示您进行确认。"

msgid "Specifies a description for a member computer."
msgstr "为成员计算机指定一个描述信息。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the NetBIOS name or fully qualified domain name (FQDN) for the Active Directory Domain Service (AD DS) domain that contains a replication group.\n"
"If you do not specify this parameter, the cmdlet uses the domain of the current user."
msgstr ""
"指定包含复制组的 Active Directory 域服务（AD DS）域的 NetBIOS "
"名称或完全限定域名（FQDN）。如果不指定此参数，cmdlet 将使用当前用户的域。"

msgid ""
"Specifies an array of names of replication groups.\n"
"You can use a comma separated list and the wildcard character (*).\n"
"If you do not specify this parameter, the cmdlet uses all participating replication groups."
msgstr "指定一个复制组名称的数组。您可以使用逗号分隔的列表以及通配符（*）。如果您不指定此参数，该cmdlet将使用所有参与的复制组。"

msgid ""
"Shows what would happen if the cmdlet runs.\n"
"The cmdlet is not run."
msgstr "展示了如果该cmdlet被运行会发生什么情况。但实际上，这个cmdlet并没有被运行。"

